   to new packaging, the effort will feature a new track dubbed "The Squeeze"
   which the band recorded exclusive for the effort, plus covers of Faith No
   More&#039;s "Epic" and The Descendents&#039; "Clean Sheets". This re-issue includes 40
   exclusive photographs and new artwork along with ten exclusive videos,
   including 3 live performances, five individual band profiles, two behind the
   scenes touring clips and a guitar lesson will round out the effort.
